title: Officemate Heavy Duty 2-Hole Punch, Padded Handle, Black, 50-Sheet Capacity (90082), Model Number: OIC90082
description: Heavy-duty, two-hole punch offers padded lock-down handle and punches 1/4" holes in up to 50 sheets of 20 lb. paper without the threat of jamming. Hole punch also features adjustable paper guide and sturdy metal construction.
